# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in real values locally.
# NO real secrets are committed to this template — only documented variable names.
#
# ─── Client (Vite-exposed) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only VITE_-prefixed vars are bundled into the public client build, so ONLY
# publishable (non-secret) values may use this prefix.
# NOTE: Vite inlines `import.meta.env.VITE_*` from `.env*` files (e.g. `.env.local`),
# NOT from this `.dev.vars` file (a Worker-only file). `setup.mjs` therefore writes the
# client publishable key into the gitignored `.env.local` so the SPA bundle picks it up;
# this line stays for documentation of the Worker-visible name only.
# Clerk publishable key — wired in Phase 3:
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# ─── Server (never VITE_-prefixed) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Server-side secrets must NOT be VITE_-prefixed and must NOT be imported into
# src/client. In production set them with `wrangler secret put <NAME>`, not here.
#
# Clerk SECRET key (Phase 3, AUTH-04/D-16) — the edge session-verification secret.
# In production set it ONLY via `wrangler secret put CLERK_SECRET_KEY` (never commit
# a real value, never add it to wrangler.jsonc). Leave empty here.
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=
#
# Clerk PUBLISHABLE key for the WORKER (Phase 3, RESEARCH Pitfall 4). The edge
# `authenticateRequest()` needs the publishable key too (to derive the FAPI URL and
# dev/prod mode) — NOT just the secret. This is the SAME `pk_…` value as
# VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY above, but WITHOUT the `VITE_` prefix so it stays on the
# Worker and never enters the client bundle. Non-secret; mirrored as a `vars` sentinel
# in wrangler.jsonc. Leave empty here.
CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
#
# Resend API key for the DORMANT async layer (Phase 7, ASYNC-03). Mirrors
# CLERK_SECRET_KEY: a server-only secret, NEVER VITE_-prefixed, NEVER committed with a
# value. Set it ONLY at async-layer activation via `wrangler secret put RESEND_API_KEY`
# (see docs/async-layer.md). The async layer ships dormant, so this stays empty unless
# you activate. Leave empty here.
RESEND_API_KEY=
